# 🤖 Production RAG System

A production-grade Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) system for intelligent document Q&A.

## 🌐 Live Demo

**Try it now:** ["https://rag-system-srvr.streamlit.app/"]

## ✨ Features

- 📄 **PDF Processing:** Upload and process any PDF document
- 🧠 **AI-Powered:** Uses OpenAI GPT-4 and embeddings
- 🔍 **Semantic Search:** ChromaDB vector database for accurate retrieval
- 🎯 **Advanced Retrieval:** Query rewriting and re-ranking
- 📊 **Metrics:** Real-time performance tracking
- ⚡ **Fast:** Sub-6 second response times
- 💰 **Cost-Effective:** ~$0.001 per query

## 📊 Performance

Based on evaluation of 20 test queries:

| Metric | Score |
|--------|-------|
| Answer Quality | 8.9/10 |
| Retrieval Accuracy (F1) | 88.4% |
| Average Latency | 5.67s |
| Cost per Query | $0.0009 |

## 🏗️ Architecture

User Query → Query Rewriter → Vector Search → Re-Ranker → GPT-4 → Answer + Sources


## 🚀 Tech Stack

- **Frontend:** Streamlit
- **LLM:** OpenAI GPT-4 & text-embedding-3-small
- **Vector DB:** ChromaDB
- **Backend:** Python 3.11
- **Deployment:** Streamlit Cloud

## 📁 Project Structure
production-rag-system/
├── app.py                  # Streamlit UI
├── src/
│   ├── document_loader.py  # PDF processing
│   ├── text_chunker.py     # Text splitting
│   ├── embeddings.py       # OpenAI embeddings
│   ├── vector_store.py     # ChromaDB interface
│   ├── retriever.py        # Semantic search
│   ├── query_rewriter.py   # Query enhancement
│   ├── reranker.py         # Result re-ranking
│   ├── qa_generator.py     # Answer generation
│   ├── rag_system.py       # Main system
│   └── monitoring.py       # Metrics tracking
├── evaluation/             # Evaluation framework
└── tests/                  # Unit tests

## 🎯 Use Cases

- **Document Q&A:** Ask questions about your documents
- **Research Assistant:** Quickly find information in papers
- **Knowledge Base:** Build searchable knowledge bases
- **Customer Support:** Automated document-based support


